        .questions
          ul#w-node-_9db26f12-9c3e-f98e-894d-6495eedf2197-af49edc1.question-list(role="list")
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_9db26f12-9c3e-f98e-894d-6495eedf2199-af49edc1 How fast will I get my site built?
              .question-icon#w-node-_9ed69bdd-0c3e-0638-702b-34014f9ec34d-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_9db26f12-9c3e-f98e-894d-6495eedf219b-af49edc1 Most requests are completed in 48–72 hours. Bigger, more complex builds (like multi-page sites or custom React projects) may take a bit longer—but we’ll keep you updated inside Trello every step of the way.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_3b36ba19-d56c-0254-b9bd-42950713b6d5-af49edc1 How does onboarding work?
              .question-icon#w-node-_3b36ba19-d56c-0254-b9bd-42950713b6d7-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_3b36ba19-d56c-0254-b9bd-42950713b6d8-af49edc1 Once you subscribe, we’ll send an invite to your private Trello board—usually within the hour.<br>You drop your Figma link, choose your preferred tech (Webflow, React, HTML/CSS), and we get to work.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-b0f58bab-3dba-58c9-1686-0b34f6e436a8-af49edc1 Who’s doing the development?
              .question-icon#w-node-b0f58bab-3dba-58c9-1686-0b34f6e436aa-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-b0f58bab-3dba-58c9-1686-0b34f6e436ab-af49edc1 This isn’t a massive team or some agency farm. It’s a tight, focused operation run by a developer—you’ll work directly with me. No handoffs, no outsourcing, no missed details.<br><br>
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-ca1700f6-b363-9da6-962e-9061a271ea7c-af49edc1 Can I queue multiple tasks?
              .question-icon#w-node-ca1700f6-b363-9da6-962e-9061a271ea7e-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-ca1700f6-b363-9da6-962e-9061a271ea7f-af49edc1 Absolutely. You can add unlimited requests to your Trello board.<br>We’ll work through them one at a time, in the priority order you set.<br><br>
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_2dcadb75-6e30-b08e-96c2-205563234d92-af49edc1 How does the pause feature work?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_2dcadb75-6e30-b08e-96c2-205563234d94-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_2dcadb75-6e30-b08e-96c2-205563234d95-af49edc1 Not busy this month? You can pause anytime.<br>Your billing cycle is based on 31 days—use what you need, then pause and return whenever you’re ready. You’ll keep any unused days.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_9cfcddbd-8b69-ebf8-f448-f69fd68d4963-af49edc1 What happens with larger builds?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_9cfcddbd-8b69-ebf8-f448-f69fd68d4965-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_9cfcddbd-8b69-ebf8-f448-f69fd68d4966-af49edc1 Larger projects are broken into manageable chunks. You’ll receive steady updates—every 48–72 hours—until the full build is completed.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_9cfcddbd-8b69-ebf8-f448-f69fd68d4963-af49edc1 What tech stacks do you support?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_9cfcddbd-8b69-ebf8-f448-f69fd68d4965-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_9cfcddbd-8b69-ebf8-f448-f69fd68d4966-af49edc1 We specialize in Webflow, React, HTML/CSS/JS, and modern front-end builds. Fast, clean, and built to scale.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_09b06569-d508-dda0-3370-1fd80d97c6da-af49edc1 How does Webflow development work?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_09b06569-d508-dda0-3370-1fd80d97c6dc-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_09b06569-d508-dda0-3370-1fd80d97c6dd-af49edc1 If your design fits within Webflow’s capabilities, we’ll build it in Webflow and hand over full ownership once it’s done.<br>That means you can manage your site moving forward—no need to stay subscribed.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_37af9f78-6b09-d982-fe26-a6de42d6c06d-af49edc1 How do I send in requests?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_37af9f78-6b09-d982-fe26-a6de42d6c06f-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_37af9f78-6b09-d982-fe26-a6de42d6c070-af49edc1 You can submit dev tasks directly through Trello.<br>Most clients drop in Figma links.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_8bfe9fe0-abe2-5542-09df-4adc23e57493-af49edc1 What if I need something revised?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_8bfe9fe0-abe2-5542-09df-4adc23e57495-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_8bfe9fe0-abe2-5542-09df-4adc23e57496-af49edc1 Revisions are always included. We’ll keep improving your build until you’re completely satisfied with the final result.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-d23363c9-071c-72f9-974d-1ef51c39a012-af49edc1 Are there any requests you don’t handle?
              .question-icon#w-node-d23363c9-071c-72f9-974d-1ef51c39a014-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-d23363c9-071c-72f9-974d-1ef51c39a015-af49edc1 Yes, here’s what we don’t do:<br>- Backend development<br>- WordPress or plugin-heavy stacks<br>- Shopify or eCommerce platforms<br>- Advanced animation frameworks (Lottie, GSAP, etc.)<br>- Rebuilding broken legacy sites with messy code<br><br>We focus on clean, modern front-end work that moves fast.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_33803f88-c478-7b34-4334-a92ca604aead-af49edc1 What if I only need one site?
              .question-icon#w-node-_33803f88-c478-7b34-4334-a92ca604aeaf-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_33803f88-c478-7b34-4334-a92ca604aeb0-af49edc1 That’s perfectly fine. You can subscribe, send your project, then pause the plan when you’re done.<br>No pressure. Come back when you’ve got more to ship.
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_1093a290-7789-14fe-6ebc-1220941e1d23-af49edc1 Do you offer refunds?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_1093a290-7789-14fe-6ebc-1220941e1d25-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_1093a290-7789-14fe-6ebc-1220941e1d26-af49edc1 Because this is a high-output service with limited spots, refunds aren’t available.<br>However, we’ll always work with you to make sure you’re happy with the outcome.<br><br>
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_28cb7edf-c09b-63d4-d0a6-fb79b6f1f6cb-af49edc1 Can I just use it for one month?<br>
              .question-icon#w-node-_28cb7edf-c09b-63d4-d0a6-fb79b6f1f6cd-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_28cb7edf-c09b-63d4-d0a6-fb79b6f1f6ce-af49edc1 Yes. Whether you need one month or one year, it’s totally up to you.<br>Subscribe when you need dev done. Pause or cancel when you don’t.<br>
            li.question-item(data-text-split="")
              p.paragraph-20#w-node-_2eecef58-c300-e2aa-e6a9-e11b2d22f1b6-af49edc1 Do you offer design?
              .question-icon#w-node-_2eecef58-c300-e2aa-e6a9-e11b2d22f1b9-af49edc1
              p.paragraph-secondary.question-paragraph#w-node-_2eecef58-c300-e2aa-e6a9-e11b2d22f1ba-af49edc1 No, but we've collaborated with web designers that can help you with what you need.
